data.message:
I'm not fussy on which day I'd get to go. I'd feel truly blessed to be able to just be there! 🙏🏻 The whole line up is incredible and it would definitely be a night to remember! 
I got to go to Summertime ball and was lucky enough to be in the gold circle. It was so much fun and we brought as much of fun and atmosphere the to the crowd there!
So, if I have to write a day, Saturday 9th December, or Sunday 10th December would be equally phenomenal! 😊
